sources.description:
Murder was easy...this girl was tough...to solve!
An English woman asks an American detective visiting London to help find her brother's killer.

Original title: Lady in the Fog (1952)  AKA: Scotland Yard Inspector

Colorized version https://youtu.be/ePXzhU_AZ6I

Directors: Sam Newfield, Pat Jackson
Writers: Orville H. Hampton, Lester Powell
Stars: Cesar Romero, Lois Maxwell, Bernadette O'Farrell, Geoffrey Keen
Genre: Mystery
